metadata.name: The Last $upper
metadata.description:
Leonardo da Shrimpi's greatest masterpiece from a bygone era.
Long thought lost, the relic has kept researchers, shrimp cult followers and historians busy for centuries and has now finally been discovered in the deepest depths of the Metaocean.

The 1st buyer will be sent a physical version of the art piece.
A high quality 32"x 18" (80cm by 45cm) signed digital print.


1/1 Edition | 7680 x 4320 px
